result.name: The Hop House Pub & Grub

reviews.text: Reasonably priced menu. Open air , covered dining facility. Special steak night Friday, was a very reasonable HK $ 138. Cooked the way we liked it. Wife and I had no issues with food. Except....they don't serve mashed spuds. Only (good) chunky French  Fries. T.Q anyway folks.
Huge selection of beers and wines! Great service and foods are superb! Love all the waiter and waitress, specially their manager! Super nice! :)

I love this place. I stop every day after work to get a beer, La Chouffe. I cannot find it everywhere. They have actually a great selection of beers. I go also every Friday to have the nachos and a pizza, the buffalina. Pizzas are definitely better than some other places that define themselves as Italian restaurants. Ingredients are fresh and really well-balanced. 
Besides, the staff is really nice and warm. It is always a pleasure to be greeted by them even if I don’t stop to dine. Thanks for all guys! Keep it on!
They offer 10 ozs u.s. steak at hk$138.00 for every Sat, regular price from sun till Fri is 238.00.  So we just tried it today.
Very good and attentive service that is definitely 4 stars! The pub food they served was up to standard too, though I found the bbq rib and chicken a bit over cooked.

Hier hebben ze echte Belgische bieren, Duvel, Leffe, etc .. en goede bediening.
Huge selection of beers and wines! Great service and foods are superb! Love all the waiter and waitress, specially their manager! Super nice! :)

HK 'er Fusionsküch ... 🤮

Ich habe ehrlich 'n robusten Magen , 'nen gesunden Appetit, esse alles-und das gern, schrecke vor keiner "Kostprobe", in keinem Land der Welt zurück,

aber was in HK als Gourmetmenü durchgeht verschlägt selbst mir die Spucke ...
(habs 3 mal versucht) 😦

Endlich mal wieder etwas wirklich sehr leckeres - Steak mit Pommes, auf den Punkt gegart, zu 'nem erschwinglichem Preis. 😋
